OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and rain linger across
OL,6,Fsouthern Scotland and northeast
OL,7,FEngland, while heavy showers
OL,8,Fdeveloping across Wales and the
OL,9,Fmidlands. Dry elsewhere with it
OL,10,Fstaying warm in the south, but cooler
OL,11,Ffurther north across Scotland and
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FSome heavy showers across
OL,15,FWales and the midlands will ease
OL,16,Fovernight, but will continue in the
OL,17,Fsoutheast into the morning. More
OL,18,Fshowers moving into Scotland but
OL,19,Felsewhere, clear skies developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
