OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FShowers in the southeast will
OL,6,Fease, but will continue across
OL,7,Fnorthern Scotland. Dry and bright
OL,8,Felsewhere with sunny spells. Windy in
OL,9,Fthe south and feeling cooler in places.
